event: response.output_text.done
data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_03be08cb106ae65c0069c2ad452cc88194a4d3a1c71e337d43","logprobs":[],"output_index":0,"sequence_number":148,"text":"One innovative solution for reducing food waste in restaurants is the \"Smart Menu Optimization System.\" This system uses AI and data analytics to predict customer preferences and optimize menu offerings in real-time, minimizing waste from unsold dishes.\n\n**Category:** Technology\n\n**Feasibility:** 8\n\n**Resources Needed:**\n1. AI software development team\n2. Data analytics tools\n3. Customer data collection systems\n4. Integration with existing restaurant POS systems\n5. Staff training programs\n\nThis system analyzes historical sales data, current trends, and customer feedback to adjust menu items dynamically. It suggests portion sizes, ingredient substitutions, and daily specials that align with predicted demand, ensuring that restaurants prepare only what is likely to be consumed."}

